description:
Cosmopolitan.com's beauty director Carly Cardellino shares the biggest beauty stories of the year, predicts the trends we'll all be seeing in 2018, and tells us how to get in shape in two weeks (really!). Before that: Feeling sick? We've got makeup tips to help you look better. Plus, we chat about Pat McGrath Labs clothing and explain why exercise is good for your skin.
